      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（一名：《梨花斩子》）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主要角色"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "樊梨花：旦"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛丁山：老生"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛应龙：小生"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情节"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛丁山、樊梨花夫妇率兵征西，共挂头二路元帅之职，兵抵番境，与番将苏宝同战于芦花河，相持不下。先"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是薛丁山兵经玉泉山，收得义子薛应龙，年方弱冠，颇英伟出众，樊梨花亦甚爱怜之，遂带同随营效力。至"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，薛应龙因与番将交战，迷路误入白家庄，被庄主强迫招亲，迨回营，樊梨花怒其未得父母之命，私自成"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婚，且有干军纪，欲斩之以伸军律。适薛丁山至，进帐向樊梨花说情。语时，并提及从前自己临阵招亲事，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "以为事有先例，谅梨花一念己身前事，必不忍过于苟求。孰意樊梨花反被羞激成怒，谓恐唐王责其治军不严，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且防诸将效尤，必不徇情，夫妇几至反目。旋经众将士环请乞情，方允以立功自赎。既而苏宝同请得妖僧"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道二人，摆设金光魔阵，以阻唐兵。薛丁山不敢轻敌，即日往求老师父下山，相助破妖。以深悉此妖阵厉害，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临行时频嘱樊梨花，勿令薛应龙轻出，免遭不测。薛应龙急欲立功赎罪，竟私往开战冲阵，卒被妖术所困，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死于非命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第十一册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四红龙套引樊梨花同上。秦汉、窦一虎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "应龙去招亲，定斩不容情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦汉、一虎，应龙到来，叫他报门而进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。\n公子不知哪里去了，你我外面寻来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛应龙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "离了芦花河，来此是营门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见二位叔父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子你回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你母亲升帐，与往日大不相同，你要小心了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，待我回去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有我二人在此，料无大碍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有二位叔父保我，进帐就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我与你报门。\n应龙告进，公子当面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下跪何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿应龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是应龙。这几日往哪里去的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行山招亲去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，你去招亲去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我且问你：招亲可有圣上旨意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘的令箭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！一无圣旨，二无将令，私自招亲，秦汉、一虎，绑起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "樊梨花坐宝帐怒气生，\n骂声应龙小畜生！\n谁叫你私自去招亲？\n定斩奴才不徇情！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦汉绑薛应龙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛丁山上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉王旨意往西征，\n十年铠甲未离身。\n白虎关前一命归阴。\n她能提兵调动三军。\n姣儿年幼韬略精。\n常把姣儿挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "营门外绑的小姣生。\n为何捆绑在营门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "先父当年挂帅印、本帅收下樊夫人、玉泉山又收应龙子、时才仙山拜师尊、来至在辕门下能行、姣儿身犯何条律、薛应龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "爹爹有所不知情，\n孩儿言来听分明：\n因此捆绑在营门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "只为行山招亲事、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我道是犯的那皇王将令，\n却原来为的是临阵招亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "只为行山招亲事、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "只为行山招亲事、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姣儿但把心放定，\n为父进阵讲人情。\n管叫你母放儿身。\n帐下儿郎杀气生。\n把姣儿送在枉死城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "只为行山招亲事、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "进帐去先行那周公礼，\n她必然念在夫妻情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "进阵就用三二语、本帅撩衣大营进、我若讲情情不准、秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迎接王爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "秦汉、一虎往上禀，\n你就说二路元帅转回唐营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛丁山上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦汉、窦一虎",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二路元帅回营。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "秦汉、一虎一声禀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二路元帅转回唐营。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛丁山上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，王爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "迎接了王爷进唐营。\n打听那贼兵怎样动兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王爷四路去打听、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一来是夫人威名盛，\n各路闻名不敢动兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王爷后帐去歇息，\n休管妾身薛闲事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "樊夫人她倒有隔山照镜，\n就知道本帅来讲情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "未曾讲情先把罪请、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王爷此礼为何行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姣儿身犯何条律，\n为何捆绑在营门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷问的是他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷呀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王爷有所不知情，\n妾身言来听分明：\n谁叫他私自去招亲？\n因此上捆绑问斩刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我令奴才去挡头阵、招亲之事犯将令、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我道是犯的那皇王将令，\n却原来为的是临阵招亲。\n难道说樊夫人心内不明？\n曾记得大战在樊……"
        },
        {
          "character": "提起了招亲事，你我的话也难尽、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦汉、窦一虎、龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“樊”什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "樊江镇，\n樊江关前动刀兵。\n夫人见面就要提亲。\n夫人就把巧计生。\n将本帅吊至在半空层。\n本帅哭地，地原无门。\n才收夫人进了唐营。\n为什么要斩那小姣生？\n自古常言道得好：\n先人开路他后人行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "本帅领兵来对阵、那时本帅不应允、设下了离山调海阵、本帅哭天，天高不允、万般无奈才允应、招亲本是你我先做、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "姻缘虽是前生定，\n五百年前结下婚。\n奴在西凉女钗裙。\n怎能够押服众三军？"
        },
        {
          "character": "你在唐营为元帅、奴才犯令若不斩、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "应龙犯罪理当斩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢王爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "还要看他年纪轻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "王爷道他年纪轻，\n有一个古人比你听：\n七岁学法九岁能。\n十三十四破曹兵。\n难道说小奴才不是娘生？"
        },
        {
          "character": "三国中有个周公瑾、十一十二为元帅、他也是人生父母养、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "本帅进帐讲人情，\n哪个与你比古人。\n二夫人亦有后代根。\n才收应龙作螟蛉。\n拿我应龙当下人。\n唐营道你两样心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大夫人也有亲生子、就是夫人身无孕、如今夫人有了孕、你今斩了应龙子、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日不斩应龙子，\n唐皇降罪谁担承？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你今赦了应龙子，\n唐王降罪有我担承。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要斩要斩偏要斩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不能不能万不能！"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你把二路元帅看大了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平息侯也不在本帅心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "樊梨花怒气生，\n秦汉、一虎听分明：\n有人讲情照令行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "平西宝剑营门挂、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见宝剑挂营门，\n唬得本帅胆战惊。\n本帅头上管三分。\n父子们做鬼一路行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "圣上赐她三尺剑、眼睁睁薛应龙不能救、我的儿吓、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我好似酒醉方才醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛应龙，我的儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他父子哭得好伤情。\n又恐怕伤了夫妻情。\n又恐三军不讲情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "本当要斩应龙子、本当不斩应龙子、左难右难难坏我、四红龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等俱以皆服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，众将皆服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，众将服了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四红龙套、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位将军请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "嗳嗳嗳，夫人，我的儿吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看王爷饶恕了小畜生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解下捆来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见营门来松绑，\n好似死里又逃生。\n谢谢母亲不斩恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将身且把宝帐进、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见奴才怒气生，\n不由为娘动无明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "手使宝剑要尔命、薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，饶过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那一旁谢过了老爹尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛应龙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谢过母亲遵了命，\n转身再谢老爹尊。\n探探贼子发来兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛应龙下。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启元帅：芦花河摆下无名大阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，芦花河摆下了无名大阵，你我夫妻到敌楼观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "时才探马报一声，\n芦花河贼子发来兵。\n看看那贼子发来兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、僧人、道人同上，同探阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，此乃什么阵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃金……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噤声！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫声夫人莫高声，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（僧人、道人、四青袍同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休要惊动那贼兵。\n夫妻们商议退贼兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人，方才城楼之上，说什么“金”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "下得马来把帐进、樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金光大阵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可能得破？"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢说你我夫妻，就是大罗神仙，难以得破。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待本帅去到仙山，求来法宝，再破此阵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷几时起程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即时起程。我有几句言语，你要牢牢谨记。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛丁山",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手挽手儿站营门，\n尊声梨花樊夫人：\n莫叫应龙去出兵。\n那时失了夫妻情。\n嘱咐你言和语你要牢记心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛丁山下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊梨花",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见王爷上马行，\n大小三军听分明：\n莫叫少爷去出兵。\n等候了王爷回再去交兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（樊梨花、四红龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
